Output term.gif
Set FontSize 17
Set Width 1100
Set Height 620
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 12
Set TypingSpeed 35ms
Hide
Type "export PATH=$PATH PS1='$ ' && clear"
Enter
Show
Type "# see what your agent actually did — locally"
Sleep 800ms
Enter
Type "tracelet --no-open &"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 2s
Type "node examples/demo.js"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 2.5s
